{"tid":1885953,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國民黨主席候選人：受武漢肺炎影響 應暫緩黨主席選舉","createTime":"2020-02-18T15:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T16:20:15.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f467af94235dee72943f0b3aea09367b6bcce7a","tid":1885953,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071819&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=1d5b28e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3071819&h=423f6041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3071819</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者施曉光／台北報導〕由於國內出現疑似社區感染案例，國民黨主席補選候選人郝龍斌今天下午一度發出新聞稿指出，當政府宣布國內疫情進入社區感染，中央防疫升級，國民黨應該立即暫緩黨主席補選，引發議論，半個多小時後，郝龍斌辦公室又補充說明，「若有大規模的社區感染發生後」，才必須考慮暫緩黨主席補選。<br />\n<br />\n郝龍斌第一時間在新聞稿中表示，國內現在出現新冠肺炎的首例死亡病例，而且疑似社區感染，連前疾管局長蘇益仁都建議，整體防疫應該提高到國安層級，他呼籲政府要重視這個社群感染的傾向，儘早做好萬全準備，一旦進入社區感染，才不會造成民眾的恐慌；全民也要投入防疫作戰，確保全民健康、維護國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n郝龍斌並鄭重呼籲，當政府宣布國內疫情進入社區感染，中央防疫升級，已屬國安問題，國民黨應該立即暫緩黨主席補選，投入全民防疫作戰，直到政府解除社區感染，再行恢復補選事宜，他還說，人命關天，防疫優先，希望各界放下個人立場，全民投入防疫作戰。<br />\n<br />\n對於郝龍斌第一時間的呼籲，國民黨文傳會代理主委王育敏回應，中央疫情指揮中心已經說明只有零星個案，甚至還呼籲一般人平常不需要戴口罩，如果未來中央疫情指揮中心宣布防疫進入新的狀況，宣導民眾不要參加公眾集會活動，國民黨會再做考量。<br />\n<br />\n王育敏說，是否暫停選舉活動，必須開會討論，黨中央尊重個別候選人意見。"},{"pid":"9b8602b15891447b35ff6e711ecfe77ad6adbacc","tid":1885953,"uid":119232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"大陸未指示要選邊個？"},{"pid":"ed4da0f57ee25e5ec4bd9916050a84692459a8a2","tid":1885953,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家快啲follow我IG page啦！<br />\n會有最新文宣，新聞同活動睇㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> IG: save_hong_kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b5f712e99310b22ab462629fdef60b3f29517e4d","tid":1885953,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b8602b15891447b35ff6e711ecfe77ad6adbacc","tid":1885953,"uid":119232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"大陸未指示要選邊個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"真係冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n選唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27c753a0fc62d34369a1833dbf1120fe53c58a3","tid":1885953,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"怕輸咋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8562edb3cdcf645204d009a5ebd2d38c222d1274","tid":1885953,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"台灣哥邊wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0d80d2f1e03fcb4308c66bd1dc20cc704e53e0","tid":1885953,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b8602b15891447b35ff6e711ecfe77ad6adbacc","tid":1885953,"uid":119232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"大陸未指示要選邊個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"唔通大陸啲領導人????"},{"pid":"6607760e103944348bf6b471b5f80e687f6fdf29","tid":1885953,"uid":81151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"執柒咗去啦"},{"pid":"4f3bdfea3714c241b930f980dae06a3e6b34a724","tid":1885953,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"防疫關你國民黨撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\